   Marketing &amp; Media:
   Time Warner Posts Loss of $51 Million
   For Quarter, Cities Costs Tied to Merger
   ----
   By Laura Landro
   Staff Reporter of The Wall Street Journal
</HL>
<DATE>
04/24/90
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), PAGE B6
</SO>
